     C* GOTO/TAG loop: sum 1..5 into RPGRET. Expected exit 15.
     C                     Z-ADD0         CNT
     C                     Z-ADD0         RPGRET
     C           LOOP      TAG
     C                     ADD  1         CNT
     C                     ADD  CNT       RPGRET
     C           CNT       COMP 5                        99
     C  N99                GOTO LOOP
